Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.51,0:03:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't we take down Moria?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not Out of Danger Yet!\NOrders to Annihilate the Straw Hat Crew!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.22,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their bodies are vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Didn't we win?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang it! Were we too late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're vanishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.22,0:05:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we won, darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.90,0:05:28.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Pirate Ship on the Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.66,0:05:27.12,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:28.51,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.21,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the deck, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit being stupid and hit the hay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.59,0:05:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning light will fry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been two years since Moria\Nstole our shadows. We'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.78,0:05:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Captain, please take a look at my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have... a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.39,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet your shadow has also returned, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.15,0:06:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-O-Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our shadows are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.79,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone, Captain!\NAll of our shadows have come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, do you think someone defeated Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.54,0:06:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so powerful that he went up\Nagainst Kaido of the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who could possibly take out Moria?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:33.86,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere in the West Blue\Non the Grand Line"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back! I have a shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been\Nsince I've seen the light of day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our zombies in Thriller Bark\Nfinally kicked the bucket!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.62,0:06:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're free from Moria's curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can watch the sunrise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! I have a shadow! It's following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a reflection!\NI can see myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was all that\Ncommotion about, Margarita?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.28,0:07:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My shadow! My shadow has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.78,0:07:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Your shadow has returned?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As in the shadow that was stolen\Nby pirates ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.96,0:07:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so surprised that I accidentally\Ndropped your prized dishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true I had hard feelings\Ntowards plates, but I've reformed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.14,0:07:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really sorry. I will leave\Nthe manor immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.44,0:08:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about those plates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, this calls for a celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is truly wonderful, Margarita.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.09,0:08:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great, Margarita?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very much alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a second, I thought I\Nwas about to go to Heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good to me! If we can go together,\NI'd love to go to Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.62,0:09:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't funny, you jerks!\NWe seriously thought you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was terrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! That was bad for my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, not that I have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the morning sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of the sunrise anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can kiss goodbye to life in the dark forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like all of them are okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.67,0:09:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We nearly ceased to exist\Nwhen the morning light hit us,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but our bodies were fully restored when
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.94,0:09:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nour shadows returned just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably along the same lines of\Nhow Moria could alter a body's shape
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by manipulating its shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I make his shadow round...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Oars will turn into a ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I know is that our bodies\Nand shadows have to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.50,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Relax! This is the only time we're ever gonna have the fun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of losing our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.88,0:10:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm just glad we didn't lose anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.51,0:10:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of a sudden, I feel totally wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There any cola around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the strange creatures and phenomena\Nwe've seen since coming ashore
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were nothing more than\Na ruse put on by Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that he has been defeated,\Nthere is nothing left on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.69,0:10:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like waking from a nightmare in\Nthe morning, everything has vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, this was one nasty haunted mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.53,0:11:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hey! Wake up, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Absalom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.42,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lola!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off! I'm not going to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.68,0:11:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has already lost her shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hogback?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the record, what happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what happened to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd wager someone defeated you. Pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.82,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly,\NI have bad news about Moria-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.20,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat defeated Moria-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! Not so loud! Lower the volume!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.45,0:11:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.46,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so riled up, Hogback?\NYou should be called Rileback.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thriller Bark is of no use to me now,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.26,0:11:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't plan on spending\Nthe rest of my days as a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:11:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.31,0:12:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.27,0:12:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Luffy shrink back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.48,0:12:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He told me that after he uses the Giant Gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his body shrinks for however\Nlong he used that gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Luffy's new fighting\Nstyle is too hard on his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the enemies waiting ahead of us\Nonly continue to get stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.67,0:12:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's gonna keep pushing himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to pull our own weight better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of them still has its shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm a severely injured old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.04,0:13:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's confusing! Just pass\Nyourself off as a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.21,0:13:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the old man\Nwe met at the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it! I never dreamed I would
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,see the day I could walk under the sun again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you! How can I ever repay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.38,0:13:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Grandpa Spoil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honorary President of the Victim Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, guys! So you pulled through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.36,0:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Come to think of it,\Nwe still haven't thanked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful from the bottom of our hearts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for all the trouble we've caused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.87,0:13:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we saw all the mayhem you caused,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we figured if you couldn't do it, no one could!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in Thriller Bark's Victim Association...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will ever forget the debt we owe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.06,0:14:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is anything you'd like,\Nplease say the word!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't much,\Nbut we have some food reserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better yet, you're welcome to marry me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.90,0:14:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll pass!\N--Five men turned her down all at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.20,0:14:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's been rejected 4,449 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't need to thank us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.12,0:14:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Luffy said, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm especially interested in you!\N--We simply fought to suit our own needs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Will you marry me?\N--We just saved you while we were at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.63,0:14:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could you say that?!\NThey actually want to thank us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You should listen to her, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.06,0:14:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us do something for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.89,0:14:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't care if you\Nsaved us on the side or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're grateful that you defeated Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.32,0:14:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.90,0:15:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't you swipe\Nall of Moria's treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.74,0:15:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll load it onto your ship for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's already on...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! I forgot about something important!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.00,0:15:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.51,0:15:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had totally forgotten about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.18,0:15:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.74,0:15:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds as though my fears were justified.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.53,0:15:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, remain calm and hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During our fight with Moria...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I forgot to mention this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is one more member on this island...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of the Seven Warlords!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.76,0:16:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.51,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Warlord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.48,0:16:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are two of the Seven Warlords\Ndoing on the same island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have finally found a\Nreplacement for Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.11,0:17:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would look bad if another one of the\NSeven Warlords needed to be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still breathing, even if barely?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he is still alive, I would\Nlike to wait for his recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and let him retain his position as one\Nof the Seven Warlords for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can take further measures later.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose one Warlord after the next,\Nthe title will cease to demand respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.14,0:17:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This information must not get out to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.68,0:17:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, those pirates\Ncause nothing but trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I recognize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nearly as large as Moria,\Nthat pirate was called the "Tyrant."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Bartholomew Kuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Tyrant Kuma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the pirate whose\Ncruelty knows no bounds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what I'm saying, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.33,0:18:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not leave witnesses to testify\Nthat Straw Hat defeated Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The World Government is\Nassigning you a special mission:
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Annihilate everyone on the island,\Nincluding the Straw Hat Crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard something!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.73,0:18:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He just said "annihilate."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, wait! Is he gonna annihilate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:18:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...all of us?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got free from Moria's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.95,0:19:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! We can't fight two Warlords in a row!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.24,0:19:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took all we had just to defeat Moria.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get back! I'll take him on!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.77,0:19:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful! He uses some sort of power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.44,0:19:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw someone vanish when\Nhe touched her with his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Negative Ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.24,0:19:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Special Hollow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The people he touches vanish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.00,0:20:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he can also warp.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the Cat Burglar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're part of the Straw Hat Crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.44,0:20:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that Monkey D. Luffy\Nhas an older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.94,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.28,0:20:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?! He got up there\Nin the blink of an eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a freak on our hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.39,0:21:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His hands... are dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.04,0:21:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.22,0:21:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When'd he get down here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.39,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I'd definitely call that warping.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We were finally set free!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.74,0:21:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no way I'm gonna die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.28,0:22:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll never let someone stand\Nbetween us and our voyage ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.79,0:22:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you heard them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.12,0:22:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.54,0:22:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, men! You don't stand a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He pierced through the whole group\Nwithout even touching all of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.47,0:23:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate Hunter Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will start with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is with the padding\Non the palms of his hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It repels all of my attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.33,0:23:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my ability. Your time's up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.75,0:23:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When it rains, it pours."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.15,0:23:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, then that shows the limit of my ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.77,0:23:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.26,0:23:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It Repels Everything!\NKuma's Paw-Paw Power!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.15,0:23:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
